Package org.apache.freemarker.core.model.impl

Data model and template language type system: Standard implementations.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    JavaMethodModel
    Common super interface (marker interface) for TemplateFunctionModel-s that stand for Java methods; do not implement it yourself! It meant to be implemented inside FreeMarker only.
    MethodAppearanceFineTuner
    Used for customizing how the methods are visible from templates, via DefaultObjectWrapper.ExtendableBuilder.setMethodAppearanceFineTuner(MethodAppearanceFineTuner).
    SingletonCustomizer
    Marker interface useful when used together with MethodAppearanceFineTuner and such customizer objects, to indicate that it doesn't contain reference to the ObjectWrapper (so beware with non-static inner classes) and can be and should be used in call introspection cache keys.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BeanAndStringModel
    Subclass of BeanModel that exposes the return value of the Object.toString() method through the TemplateStringModel interface.
    BeanModel
    A class that will wrap an arbitrary object into TemplateHashModel interface allowing calls to arbitrary property getters and invocation of accessible methods on the object from a template using the object.foo to access properties and object.bar(arg1, arg2) to invoke methods on it.
    DefaultArrayAdapter
    Adapts an array of a non-primitive elements to the corresponding TemplateModel interface(s), most importantly to TemplateHashModelEx.
    DefaultEnumerationAdapter
    Adapts an Enumeration to the corresponding TemplateModel interface(s), most importantly to TemplateIterableModel.
    DefaultIterableAdapter
    Adapts an Iterable to the corresponding TemplateModel interface(s), most importantly to TemplateIterableModel.
    DefaultIteratorAdapter
    Adapts an Iterator to the corresponding TemplateModel interface(s), most importantly to TemplateIterableModel.
    DefaultListAdapter
    Adapts a List to the corresponding TemplateModel interface(s), most importantly to TemplateSequenceModel.
    DefaultMapAdapter
    Adapts a Map to the corresponding TemplateModel interface(s), most importantly to TemplateHashModelEx.
    DefaultNonListCollectionAdapter
    Adapts a non-List Java Collection to the corresponding TemplateModel interface(s), most importantly to TemplateCollectionModel.
    DefaultObjectWrapper
    The default implementation of the ObjectWrapper interface.
    DefaultObjectWrapper.Builder
    Gets/creates a DefaultObjectWrapper singleton instance that's already configured as specified in the properties of this object; this is recommended over using the DefaultObjectWrapper constructors.
    DefaultObjectWrapper.ExtendableBuilder<ProductT extends DefaultObjectWrapper,SelfT extends DefaultObjectWrapper.ExtendableBuilder<ProductT,SelfT>>
    You will not use this abstract class directly, but concrete subclasses like DefaultObjectWrapper.Builder, unless you are developing a builder for a custom DefaultObjectWrapper subclass.
    DefaultObjectWrapperExtension
    See the extensions setting of DefaultObjectWrapper.
    MapKeyValuePairIterator
    Implementation of TemplateHashModelEx2.KeyValuePairIterator for a TemplateHashModelEx2 that wraps or otherwise uses a Map internally.
    MethodAppearanceFineTuner.Decision
    Used for MethodAppearanceFineTuner.process(org.apache.freemarker.core.model.impl.MethodAppearanceFineTuner.DecisionInput, org.apache.freemarker.core.model.impl.MethodAppearanceFineTuner.Decision) to store the results.
    MethodAppearanceFineTuner.DecisionInput
    Used for MethodAppearanceFineTuner.process(org.apache.freemarker.core.model.impl.MethodAppearanceFineTuner.DecisionInput, org.apache.freemarker.core.model.impl.MethodAppearanceFineTuner.Decision) as input parameter.
    ResourceBundleModel
    A hash model that wraps a resource bundle.
    RestrictedObjectWrapper
    A restricted version of DefaultObjectWrapper that doesn't expose arbitrary object, just those that directly correspond to the TemplateModel sub-interfaces (String, Map and such).
    RestrictedObjectWrapper.Builder  
    RestrictedObjectWrapper.ExtendableBuilder<ProductT extends RestrictedObjectWrapper,SelfT extends RestrictedObjectWrapper.ExtendableBuilder<ProductT,SelfT>>  
    SequenceTemplateModelIterator
    TemplateIterableModel implementation that can iterate through a TemplateSequenceModel be going through the valid indexes and calling TemplateSequenceModel.get(int) for each.
    SimpleCollection
    A simple implementation of TemplateCollectionModel.
    SimpleDate
    A simple implementation of the TemplateDateModel interface.
    SimpleHash
    A simple implementation of the TemplateHashModelEx interface, using its own underlying Map or SortedMap for storing the hash entries.
    SimpleIterable
    A simple implementation of TemplateIterableModel.
    SimpleJavaMethodModel
    Wraps a Method into the TemplateFunctionModel interface.
    SimpleNumber
    A simple implementation of the TemplateNumberModel interface.
    SimpleSequence
    A simple implementation of the TemplateSequenceModel interface, using its own underlying List for storing the list items.
    SimpleString
    A simple implementation of the TemplateStringModel interface, using a String.
    SingleItemTemplateModelIterator
    TemplateModelIterator for the special case when you have exactly one element.
    TemplateModelListSequence
    A sequence that wraps a List of TemplateModel-s.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DefaultObjectWrapperExtensionPhase
    Used for the return value of DefaultObjectWrapperExtension.getPhase().
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InvalidPropertyException
    An exception thrown when there is an attempt to access an invalid bean property when we are in a "strict bean" mode

Package org.apache.freemarker.core.model.impl Description

Data model and template language type system: Standard implementations. This package is part of the published API, that is, user code can safely depend on it.
